# This file overrides global Constitutional Framework rules for this project

# Docker Compose Files Exception
# This project uses multi-environment compose files by design
# Rationale: Production (blacklist.nxtd.co.kr) and Development (blacklist.jclee.me)
#            require different configurations (Traefik labels, env vars, volumes)
